std_msgs/Header header
bool detected
float64 q_y           # LOS elevation angle [rad] (valid when detected=true)
float64 q_z           # LOS azimuth angle [rad] (valid when detected=true)
float64 fov_yaw_rate  # FOV yaw rate command [rad/s] Eq.(13)
float64 fov_vel_z     # FOV Z velocity correction [m/s] (ey-based)
